      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 when validation and COU operating conditions are demonstrated to overlap.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping is not required at MRL 2. The overlap between validation operating conditions and COU operating envelope is demonstrated qualitatively through the operating point comparison documented in the relevance of validation activities factor."
