    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with Medium model influence. The comprehensive Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification demonstrates that 95th-percentile RH predictions remain below 1.0 across the full operating envelope, satisfying the regulatory acceptance criterion even under worst-case input uncertainty. The assessment is therefore accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission.",
